         <abstract>
            <p>Optimal methods for the numerical solution of Volterra integral equations of the first kind are outlined in [3] and [4]. An explicit algorithm for the construction of such methods as well as tables of coefficients for methods with order less than or equal to eight are displayed here.</p>
          </abstract>
